# jetpack-theme CSS conventions

Match the patterns in `src/components/card.css` and `src/templates/single-post.css`.

## Nesting with `&`

```css
/* ✅ GOOD — nest selectors and media queries inside their parent */
.jetpack-card-image {
  margin-bottom: 0.875rem;

  &.wp-block-post-featured-image {
    margin: 0 -1rem 0.875rem;
    border-radius: 0;

    & > a { border-radius: 0 !important; }
    & img { border-radius: 0; }
  }

  @media (min-width: 640px) { margin-bottom: 1rem; }
}

/* ❌ BAD — flat repetition of the ancestor chain */
.jetpack-card-image { margin-bottom: 0.875rem; }
.jetpack-card-image.wp-block-post-featured-image { margin: 0 -1rem 0.875rem; }
.jetpack-card-image.wp-block-post-featured-image > a { border-radius: 0 !important; }
```

## Mobile-first breakpoints

Use `min-width` queries, ordered low to high. Breakpoints in this theme:

- `@media (min-width: 640px)` — tablet
- `@media (min-width: 768px)` — large tablet
- `@media (min-width: 1024px)` — desktop
- `@media (min-width: 1280px)` — wide

For grid column overrides inside `is-layout-grid`, use paired ranges:
`(max-width: 639px)`, `(min-width: 640px) and (max-width: 1023px)`, `(min-width: 1024px)`.

## Shorthand margin / padding

```css
/* ✅ GOOD */
padding: 3rem 0.75rem 0;
margin: -4.5rem 0 0;

/* ❌ BAD */
padding-top: 3rem;
padding-left: 0.75rem;
padding-right: 0.75rem;
padding-bottom: 0;
```

## Theme tokens

Always prefer custom properties over literals:

- `var(--foreground)`, `var(--muted-foreground)`, `var(--background)`, `var(--muted)`
- `var(--border)`, `var(--accent)`, `var(--frame)`, `var(--sand)`
- `var(--header-clearance)` for top padding that clears the fixed header

## `!important` rule

Only use `!important` to override an existing `!important` from WordPress core or `components/card.css`. **Always add a comment explaining why:**

```css
/* !important overrides the `margin: 0 !important` in components/card.css */
.jetpack-card-title { margin: 0 0 0.625rem !important; }
```

## DRY shared properties

When two selectors share >3 properties, extract:

```css
/* ✅ GOOD */
.jetpack-blog-hero__title,
.jetpack-blog-hero__desc {
  color: var(--foreground);
  text-align: center;
  text-wrap: balance;
  margin-inline: auto !important;
}

.jetpack-blog-hero__title { font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.25rem); /* ... */ }
.jetpack-blog-hero__desc  { font-size: 1.125rem; /* ... */ }
```
